apps.name: JellyMuse
apps.localizedDescription: Jellyfin Music Client that mimics Apple Music

versions.localizedDescription: Pre-Release: Fixed the issue where deleting downloaded content from the settings page wouldn't actually delete content. It now deletes downloaded content and the songs listed below if you delete an album completely. In the DownloadsView, the downloaded albums from the AlbumDetailView now (should) download correctly and show up in the DownloadsView.
